Add images, videos, and text to promote your products.</p></div><div class=\"col-md-4\"><h4>PDF Linesheet Generator</h4><p>Customize your linesheet settings and download or print your presentations as PDFs. Choose the product image and information settings, font settings, pricing, paper size, orientation, layout, cover page, contact information, size grid and more.</p></div><div class=\"col-md-4\"><h4>Linesheet Templates</h4><p>Use the PDF linesheet generator to save your preferred PDF settings as templates to make future linesheets a breeze.</p></div></div><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-md-4\"><h4>Viewer Notifications</h4><p>Get notifications when buyers view your online linesheet presentations.</p></div><div class=\"col-md-4\"><h4>Password Protection</h4><p>Set custom access codes for opening your presentations to prevent your designs from being stolen. Create as many as you need and set expiration dates for each.</p></div><div class=\"col-md-4\"><h4>Presentation Settings</h4><p>Customize your presentation’s pricing display, order settings, inventory display, and prepack and discount options.</p></div></div><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-md-4\"><h4>Discounts</h4><p>Set product discounts on individual items or a group of products.</p></div><div class=\"col-md-4\"><h4>Product Labels</h4><p>Add labels like “New” and “Sale” to your products to highlight featured items.</p></div><div class=\"col-md-4\"><h4>Team/Showroom Permissions</h4><p>Hide or share presentations from certain showrooms or team members with simple settings controls.</p></div></div><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-md-4\"><h4>Presentation Organization</h4><p>Create folders and tag your presentations to make them easier to navigate.</p></div></div><div class=\"row col-sm-12\"><h3>Reports</h3></div><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-md-4\"><h4>Top Products Report</h4><p>Generate reports for your top products over a specified period of time. Easily track and determine your best-sellers.</p></div><div class=\"col-md-4\"><h4>Production Reports</h4><p>See what products are producing sales or create production reports for your manufacturers.</p></div><div class=\"col-md-4\"><h4>Orders Reports</h4><p>Run order reports to get details on all orders or orders from a specific customer.</p></div></div><div class=\"row col-sm-12\"><h3>iPad App</h3></div><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-md-4\"><h4>Offline Ordering</h4><p>The Brandboom iPad app allows for online and offline ordering on the go. Orders sync to your online account automatically.</p></div><div class=\"col-md-4\"><h4>Synced Presentations</h4><p>Download your online presentations onto your iPad to use online and offline. Present them to buyers on the spot.</p></div><div class=\"col-md-4\"><h4>Saved Customer List</h4><p>Always have your customer information on hand. Use customer codes to pre-fill your online and offline orders.</p></div></div><div class=\"row col-sm-12\"><h3>Buyer Side</h3></div><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-md-4\"><h4>Presentations Archive</h4><p>Buyers have your presentations saved to their buyer account so they can easily view and reorder any time.</p></div><div class=\"col-md-4\"><h4>Orders Status</h4><p>Buyers can keep track of orders placed or the orders you’ve sent for review. They can keep track of order statuses and pay outstanding invoices.</p></div><div class=\"col-md-4\"><h4>Saved Open Orders</h4><p>Buyers can save open orders to their account so they can complete an order at a later time without losing their information.  </p></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"row col-xs-12 text-center no-spacing visible-md visible-lg margin-top-50\"><a role=\"button\"
